description: Edit geodata and contribute to OpenStreetMap project on-the-go * Create and edit new Nodes and Ways * Move and rotate Ways * Append Nodes to existing Ways * Delete Nodes * Create, edit and delete Tags * Edit relations and create new turn restrictions * JOSM presets support * Download and Upload to OSM-Server * Saving and reading of JOSM format OSM data files * Highlight unnamed highways, and ways/nodes with todos or fixmes * Add, comment and close OSM Notes and Osmose bugs * Use a variety of background tile layers as reference * Show the users GPS-Track with accuracy * Upload to OSM and local saving of GPS tracks * Display the raw data * Display geo-referenced photographs .... and lots more. Vespucci is not a map viewer or routing-application Help and instructions are available on device and on the Vespucci website.
